to download Ubuntu go to the formal site 'https://releases.ubuntu.com/20.04/'
download the version 20.04 
then the image file of ubuntu will appear in the downloads folder.
open the file and install ubuntu in the usual way.
after the installation is over, go to the VirtualBox and create a new virtual machine with the name Ubuntu.
choice the standard setting depending on your device.
after you create the Ubuntu virtual machine click the settings button and go to the storage box, then add the ubuntu image file that we have downloaded already.
now you can start ubuntu by clicking on the start button.
